  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This registry is a data collection on patients who are implanted for more than 6 months with
      a pacemaker. Frequency and distribution of right ventricular pacing, NYHA class and left
      ventricular ejection fraction shall be documented.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
